Line1.BAB4F: Only one of us will walk away from this, so let’s enjoy the storm a moment. Ah, nature’s music.
Line11.BAE4: You’ve fallen for the demon’s lies.
Line13.BAB4F: No, no. This is my choice. Lilith only granted me the power to do what must be done.
Line15.BAE4: And what did you give her?
Line17.BAB4F: All things must be earned in the wilds, even knowledge. Prove yourself, and you will have your answers...
Line19.BAB4F: Some will die, yes...but that is the way of nature. It is a crucible. It devours the weak and makes the strong stronger. And those who survive, they will save this land from Hell.
